name: Fruits
public_notice: Fruits (FRTS) has migrated from their older ETH contract to their own original Fruits Blockchain. For more information, please view this announcement.

description.en:
Fruits is a platform where anyone can participate and be a part of with an economy that uses PoC algorithms.
It performs a sustainable economic cycle with much lower power consumption, high security, and no remittance fee is required.　
The economic cycle created by PoC provides a unique blockchain economy that aims to revitalize global charity together with athletes.
